with hard evidence

00:15:13.490 --> 00:15:15.710
on the legacy of liberals.

00:15:15.710 --> 00:15:16.630
Close quote.

00:15:16.630 --> 00:15:18.940
And so there it is, life is hard.

00:15:18.940 --> 00:15:22.670
You use the word hard,
you use the words serious,

00:15:22.670 --> 00:15:24.670
you use evidence.

00:15:24.670 --> 00:15:27.260
Tom Sowell is a man of
the constrained vision

00:15:27.260 --> 00:15:28.760
through and through and through, correct?

00:15:28.760 --> 00:15:29.740
- Yes.

00:15:29.740 --> 00:15:30.573
- No, no...

00:15:31.680 --> 00:15:32.513
- Yes.

00:15:32.513 --> 00:15:35.740
Part of a vanishing breed I might add.

00:15:35.740 --> 00:15:40.740
- So when you were a
Marxist, explain that,

00:15:41.080 --> 00:15:42.546
because the Marxism...

00:15:42.546 --> 00:15:43.702
- Well but no, no.

00:15:43.702 --> 00:15:45.178
- So that's complicated.

00:15:45.178 --> 00:15:46.011
- Even when I was a Marxist,

00:15:46.011 --> 00:15:48.700
I had the same intellectual standards

00:15:48.700 --> 00:15:51.760
and that's what eventually
